summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2826, for the improvement of the alley between 7th Avenue and 8th Avenue, running from Pine Street to Olive Street; all in the City of Seattle, by paving the same with brick, under Ordinance No. 33908 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
